---
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---
<section class="fullscreen-section" id="problem-section">
  <div class="content-container h-full flex items-center flex-col justify-center px-6 max-w-6xl w-full">
    <div id="hero-headline" class="text-5xl md:text-7xl text-white mb-6 leading-tight text-center">
        Das Problem der
        <br />
        <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#FF0000] via-[#FF0000] to-[#FFA500] bg-clip-text text-transparent ">
          Digital Humanities
        </span>
    </div>
    <div>
      <span class="text-gray-200 font-medium max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center mb-12 block leading-relaxed">
        In den digitalen Geisteswissenschaften dominieren bislang digitale Editionen und punktuelle "Insel-Lösungen" – Tools und Skripte, die nur für ein spezifisches Forschungsproblem entwickelt wurden.
      </span>
    </div>
    <!-- Problem Section Grid-->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mt-4 w-full">


      <!-- First Container -->
      <div class="border-2 border-gray-700 bg-gray-800/20 rounded-xl p-6 flex flex-col max-w-lg">
        <div class="flex flex-row items-center space-x-4 mb-6">
          <!-- Icon Container -->
          <div class="bg-red-400/20 p-2 rounded-lg">
            <Icon name="lucide:database" size={24} class="text-red-400" />
          </div>
          <!-- Text Container -->
           <div id="problem-headline" class="text-lg">
            <span class="text-white font-bold text-xl">Fragmentierte Datenlandschaft</span>
           </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Description -->
        <div class="-mt-2">
          <span class="text-gray-300 text-sm">Historische Daten sind über verschiedene Systeme verstreut und schwer zugänglich</span>
        </div>
      </div>


      <!-- Second Container -->
      <div class="border-2 border-gray-700 bg-gray-800/20 rounded-xl p-6 flex flex-col max-w-lg">
        <div class="flex flex-row items-center space-x-4 mb-6">
          <!-- Icon Container -->
          <div class="bg-red-400/20 p-2 rounded-lg">
            <Icon name="lucide:trending-down" size={24} class="text-red-400" />
          </div>
          <!-- Text Container -->
           <div id="problem-headline" class="text-lg">
            <span class="text-white font-bold text-xl">Ineffiziente Workflows</span>
           </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Description -->
        <div class="-mt-2">
          <span class="text-gray-300 text-sm">Manuelle Prozesse verlangsamen die Forschung und führen zu Datenverlusten</span>
        </div>
      </div>


      <!-- Third Container -->
      <div class="border-2 border-gray-700 bg-gray-800/20 rounded-xl p-6 flex flex-col max-w-lg">
        <div class="flex flex-row items-center space-x-4 mb-6">
          <!-- Icon Container -->
          <div class="bg-red-400/20 p-2 rounded-lg">
            <Icon name="lucide:repeat" size={24} class="text-red-400" />
          </div>
          <!-- Text Container -->
           <div id="problem-headline" class="text-lg">
            <span class="text-white font-bold text-xl">Fehlende Reproduzierbarkeit</span>
           </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Description -->
        <div class="-mt-2">
          <span class="text-gray-300 text-sm">Forschungsergebnisse sind schwer nachvollziehbar und nicht FAIR-konform, was auch die Wiederverwendbarkeit der Daten einschränkt</span>
        </div>
      </div>


      <!-- Fourth Container -->
      <div class="border-2 border-gray-700 bg-gray-800/20 rounded-xl p-6 flex flex-col max-w-lg">
        <div class="flex flex-row items-center space-x-4 mb-6">
          <!-- Icon Container -->
          <div class="bg-red-400/20 p-2 rounded-lg">
            <Icon name="lucide:chart-no-axes-combined" size={24} class="text-red-400" />
          </div>
          <!-- Text Container -->
           <div id="problem-headline" class="text-lg">
            <span class="text-white font-bold text-xl">Begrenzte Skalierbarkeit</span>
           </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Description -->
        <div class="-mt-2">
          <span class="text-gray-300 text-sm">Aktuelle Tools können nicht mit der wachsenden Datenmenge mithalten und sind nicht für die Zukunft gerüstet</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>



<style>
  #hero-headline {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 900; /* Extra bold */
  }
  #problem-headline {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 800; /* Bold */
  }

  .hero-badge {
    position: relative;
    transform-origin: center;
  }

  .hero-badge::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -2px;
    left: -2px;
    right: -2px;
    bottom: -2px;
    background: linear-gradient(45deg, #3b82f6, #8b5cf6, #f59e0b, #06b6d4);
    background-size: 300% 300%;
    border-radius: inherit;
    z-index: -1;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.5s ease;
    animation: gradient-shift 3s ease infinite;
  }

  .hero-badge:hover::before {
    opacity: 0.3;
  }

  .hero-badge:hover {
    transform: scale(1.02);
    border-color: transparent;
  }
.hero-badge:hover span {
    font-weight: 500;
    color: white;
  }
  @keyframes gradient-shift {
    0% {
      background-position: 0% 50%;
    }
    50% {
      background-position: 100% 50%;
    }
    100% {
      background-position: 0% 50%;
    }
  }
</style>